ygData.subject: Underwater dw gob city in lake rathe

ygData.messageBody:
the other day as my friends and I were killing aviak guards in lakerathe
we came upon a passageway under 3 bird island, I stripped off my
equipment and let someone else hold it, got an enduring breath and went
down to explore, inside it opened up into a large underwater cavern, the
only structure I found within was what appreared to be a tower guarded
by 6 dw gobs with a trausre chest inside and something else I didn't get
a look at, does anyone know anything about this? I would sure like to
know more, from what I've heard from the few people who've even heard of
it, it leads to a dw gob city. if anyone knows anything about it please
e-mail me, I also have screenshots of what I saw. thanks.
